				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I&#8217;m a Hillary Clinton supporter. I was in 2008, I was earlier this year, and absolutely <a href="http://www.manton.org/2016/07/this-is-hillarys-week.html">I am now</a>, as Donald Trump seems intent with each daily blunder to prove he&#8217;s the worst candidate the Republicans have fielded in quite some time.</p>
